snippet.title: Noble Fates Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1769420/Noble_Fates/

Early Access on December 14th, 2021

Noble Fates is a 3D Fantasy Kingdom Sim driven by intelligent characters with a rich simulation of opinions and memories. Command from the sky or take control in third person as your story goes where the people, your actions, and their reactions take it.

Discord: https://discord.gg/HeAaQcS
